B. At the same time, regional instability may make a resolution of the
                        Iranian problem more difficult for us, and it could bring us into a head to
                        head confrontation with the Soviets;

C. SALT is likely to be damaged, perhaps
                        irreparably, because Soviet military aggressiveness will have been so
                        naked;

A. It is essential that Afghanistani resistance continues. This means more
                        money as well as arms shipments to the rebels, and some technical
                        advice;
